branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VNA series is a universal 2 port valve used for controlling pneumatic systems or air-hydro circuits. Its balanced poppet design permits normal and reverse flow application.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External pilot solenoid type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compatible with wide range of gas and oil&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating pressure range: 0 to 1.0 MPa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.88 to 43&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coil rated voltage: AC(50/60Hz) 100V, 200V, DC 24V, others optional&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluid temperature: -5 to 60&#xb0;C (no freezing)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

